                "affiliation": "Social Information Systems, Open University"
            }
        ],
        "cbStatement": "Our work exposes gender-based stereotypes expressed through linguistic biases, illustrates the forms in which they manifest, and raises implications for those who design systems or train algorithms using data produced via GWAP.",
        "keywords": "Crowdsourcing; Games with a Purpose; gender; linguistic bias; metadata; stereotypes; subjective language",
        "venue": "Paper",
        "subtype": "Paper",
        "award": 0,
        "hm": 0
