            }
        ],
        "cbStatement": "We present results from a field study at three manufacturing sites examining the social relationship between a collaborative manufacturing robot and human workers.",
        "keywords": "Computer-Supported Collaborative Work; Human-Robot Collaboration; Collaborative Robots; Technology Adoption; Manufacturing; Sociality; Social Cues; Design Guidelines",
