                "location": "London, United Kingdom",
                "affiliation": "University College London"
            }
        ],
        "cbStatement": "We present a methodology for evaluating serious experience in digital games and discuss how our methods enabled a consideration of gameplay in terms of immediate and longer term impact.",
        "keywords": "Games; evaluation; critical play; engagement; positive experience; negative experience; serious experience",
        "venue": "Paper",
