        "cbStatement": "We propose a novel paradigm to assess the sensory-motor similarity between HCIs based on transfer of learning, and provide a first indication of the naturalness of various HCIs.",
        "keywords": "transfer of learning; sensory-motor skill; interaction similarity; NUI; naturalness; empirical methods; motor learning",
        "venue": "Paper",
