                "affiliation": "University College London"
            }
        ],
        "cbStatement": "We explored how the gym context influenced people's adoption, use and non-use of digital technologies for purposes ranging from tracking to entertainment during individual physical activity.",
        "keywords": "health; fitness; exercise; gym; situated studies; in the wild; wearables; activity tracker; personal informatics; context",
