            }
        ],
        "cbStatement": "This paper contributes a spreadsheet model for using streaming data, introducing novel ways to stream data from web sources, control streaming timing and manipulate data using temporal information in spreadsheets. ",
        "keywords": "Spreadsheets; streaming data; web services; end-user pro-gramming; live programming",
